Package com.github.btrekkie.programmatic_image

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IProgrammaticImageRenderer
    A rectangular image where we may render an aribtrary subrectangle at an arbitrary zoom.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ProgrammaticImageCache
    Caches different subrectangles of an image at different zooms, e.g.
    ProgrammaticImageComponent
    A JComponent that renders an IProgrammaticImageRenderer image.
    ProgrammaticImageFrame
    A JFrame that renders an IProgrammaticImageRenderer image, along with zoom buttons and scroll bars.
    ProgrammaticImageRect
    A subrectangle region of an IProgrammaticImageRendererImage, along with a level of zoom.
    ProgrammaticImageResult
    An entry in a ProgrammaticImageCache: a region of an IProgrammaticImageRenderer image along with the BufferedImage result of rendering the region.
    ProgrammaticImageWorker
    A SwingWorker for rendering a region of an IProgrammaticImageRenderer image.
